---
// AI-Assisted PDF Reports - Visual Showcase of Features and Benefits
---

<section class="pdf-showcase-section">
  <div class="showcase-container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Quarterly Inspection Reports</p>
      <h2>What's included in your report</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Each quarterly inspection includes a professional PDF report designed for property owners.
        Our AI reviews photos and tells you exactly what needs fixing ‚Äî and who should fix it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Visual Split: Before/After or Problem/Solution -->
    <div class="comparison-container">
      <!-- Left: Old Way (Problem) -->
      <div class="comparison-side old-way">
        <div class="side-label label-old">DIY Documentation</div>
        <div class="side-content">
          <div class="problem-icon">üìã</div>
          <h3 class="side-title">Doing It Yourself</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list problem-list">
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚ùå</span>
              <span class="item-text">Takes time out of your busy schedule</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚ùå</span>
              <span class="item-text">Easy to miss issues without training</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚ùå</span>
              <span class="item-text">No consistent documentation format</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚ùå</span>
              <span class="item-text">Photos scattered across devices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚ùå</span>
              <span class="item-text">Hard to track changes over time</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="time-badge badge-slow">
            <span class="time-icon">‚è∞</span>
            <span class="time-text">Time-consuming and inconsistent</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Divider with Arrow -->
      <div class="comparison-divider">
        <div class="divider-arrow">‚Üí</div>
        <div class="divider-text">Choose Smarter</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: New Way (Solution) -->
      <div class="comparison-side new-way">
        <div class="side-label label-new">CheckMyRental Service</div>
        <div class="side-content">
          <div class="solution-icon">‚úÖ</div>
          <h3 class="side-title">Inspection + AI Report</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list solution-list">
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚úÖ</span>
              <span class="item-text">Professional cover page with property details</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚úÖ</span>
              <span class="item-text">To-Do List separates tenant vs owner fixes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚úÖ</span>
              <span class="item-text">Photo pages with AI analysis side-by-side</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚úÖ</span>
              <span class="item-text">Simple language anyone can understand</span>
            </li>
            <li class="feature-item">
              <span class="item-icon">‚úÖ</span>
              <span class="item-text">Clear urgency tags: Fix Now vs Fix Soon</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="time-badge badge-fast">
            <span class="time-icon">üìÑ</span>
            <span class="time-text">Ready to share with tenants</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why It's Smarter Section -->
    <div class="why-smarter-section">
      <h3 class="smarter-title">What Makes Our Reports Different</h3>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-number">01</div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">To-Do List Page</h4>
          <p class="benefit-text">
            The second page of your report is a simple to-do list. It separates what your tenant can fix themselves
            (like changing air filters) from what you need to hire someone for (like water damage).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-number">02</div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Easy to Understand</h4>
          <p class="benefit-text">
            We write in plain English, not inspector jargon. Many property owners are busy or speak English as a second language.
            Our reports use simple words so everyone knows exactly what needs to be done.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-number">03</div>
          <h4 class="benefit-title">Share With Your Tenant</h4>
          <p class="benefit-text">
            The tenant section of your report is designed to share. Show your tenant what they need to take care of ‚Äî
            with clear explanations like "buy a new air filter at the hardware store."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pdf-showcase-section {
    padding: 120px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #0f0f0f 50%, #0a0a0a 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .showcase-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    color: #e74c3c;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #a0a0a0;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Comparison Container */
  .comparison-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .comparison-side {
    background: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.6);
    border: 2px solid;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .old-way {
    border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
  }

  .new-way {
    border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05);
  }

  .new-way:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
  }

  .side-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    padding: 6px 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .label-old {
    background: #dc2626;
    color: white;
  }

  .label-new {
    background: #10b981;
    color: white;
  }

  .side-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-icon,
  .solution-icon {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .side-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #d0d0d0;
  }

  .item-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .time-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .badge-slow {
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
    border: 2px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4);
    color: #ff6b6b;
  }

  .badge-fast {
    background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
    border: 2px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
    color: #34d399;
  }

  .time-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .comparison-divider {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .divider-arrow {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #ff6b6b);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);
  }

  .divider-text {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #e74c3c;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  /* Why Smarter Section */
  .why-smarter-section {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .smarter-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1));
    border: 1px solid rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit-number {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .benefit-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fafafa;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .benefit-text {
    color: #c0c0c0;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .comparison-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .comparison-divider {
      order: 2;
    }

    .old-way {
      order: 1;
    }

    .new-way {
      order: 3;
    }

    .divider-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pdf-showcase-section {
      padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .section-header h2,
    .breakdown-title,
    .smarter-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 6vw, 2.5rem);
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .features-grid,
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .comparison-container {
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .comparison-side {
      padding: 24px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
    }

    .side-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      padding: 5px 14px;
    }

    .problem-icon,
    .solution-icon {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .side-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .feature-item {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .item-icon {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .time-badge {
      padding: 10px 18px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .time-icon {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .divider-arrow {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .divider-text {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }

    .why-smarter-section {
      margin-bottom: 50px;
    }

    .smarter-title {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .benefit-card {
      padding: 28px 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .benefit-number {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .benefit-title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .benefit-text {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }

  /* Very small screens */
  @media (max-width: 360px) {
    .pdf-showcase-section {
      padding: 50px 12px;
    }

    .section-header h2,
    .smarter-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .comparison-side {
      padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .side-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .feature-item {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .benefit-card {
      padding: 24px 20px;
    }

    .benefit-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .benefit-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
